	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In hac hora tuę atque <persName ref="p1283" cert="high">Gesneri</persName> ad me et ad alios literę cum libris offeruntur, quare non licet, ut volui, ad cuncta respondere.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l157" cert="high">Frankfortum</placeName> abiturus tabellarius ne momentum expectare voluit.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Curabo, ut recte curentur omnia, libri et literę, quibus sunt inscripte, afferantur.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ago gracias pro libellis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pedagogum rogo ut primo quovis tempore mittatis.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><foreign xml:lang="de">Den frantzhosischen apothekher</foreign> desideramus; habebit conditionem se dignam non tantum apud prophanum populum, sed inserviet valetudinario... que civi podagrico in exhibendis medicinis; hunc sentiet divitem, liberalem et parentem.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Conditio nulli locabitur, sed in istius adventum differetur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">O bone deus, quanta aviditate tuas contra impanationem impiam cogitationes expectavi; eas legam diligentissime.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l619" cert="high">Bavari</placeName>, deo gloria, excusserunt iugum pontificium; data est urgentibus nobilibus et subditis communio sub utraque, libertas ciborum, conciones pię non tantum indulgendo; <foreign xml:lang="de">sunder der hertzog mueß ins landpuech schreiben,</foreign> et si ordinarii episcopii <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1725">Salisburgensis</placeName>, <placeName type="citizen_name">Aistetensis</placeName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l18">Augustanus</placeName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1706">Frisingensis</placeName> etc., ad quos pro consensu scribet princeps, recusarent, nihilominus princeps concessa velit habere rata.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed non licet plura.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Brevi mittam acta illorum comitiorum <persName type="auto_name">Bavaricorum</persName>.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hec eadem dicito <persName ref="p1283" cert="high">Gesnero</persName> nostro.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ocyssime 29. martii anno 56.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2856" cert="high">Geryon</persName> t[uus].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pientissimo atque doctissimo viro d. <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Heinricho Bullingero</persName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l587" cert="high">Tygurensis</placeName> ecclesię episcopo, domino et fratri observandissimo.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" cert="high">Zurch</placeName> in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862" cert="high">Schweitz</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
